{
  "name": "UDA Terminal Laptop",
  "author": "AgentKush",
  "version": "1.2",
  "description": "v1.2: Placement fix. The laptop now deploys (shows a placement ghost) and the Press=Workshop / Hold=Orbital Deposit interactions fire. v1.1 used BP_Terminal_C (a lore-note BP that overrides Deployable_Interact and blocked the placement preview); v1.2 uses BP_Deer_Trophy_C, the generic deployable the vanilla collectable laptop uses, which honours the data-driven Interactable trait.\n\nv1.1: Switched the deployable BP from BP_Prop_Laptop_A (static prop) to BP_Terminal_C (the vanilla placeable-laptop BP), fixing the no-preview placement bug from v1.0.\n\nv1.0: Adds a craftable UDA Terminal Laptop. Place it in your base, press F to open the Workshop, hold F to open the Orbital Deposit. Saves the walk back to the drop tube. No PAK required - uses vanilla MetaShop and SpaceInventory interaction behaviours that already exist in the game.",
  "fileName": "UDA_Terminal_Laptop",
